FBIS3-36727 "drsov027_p_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-027 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Feb 1994 CAUCASUS Armenia Government Authorized Border Trade With Iran PM0802145794 Moscow IZVESTIYA in Russian 8 Feb 94 First Edition p 3 PM0802145794 Moscow IZVESTIYA Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Report by Sergey Bablumyan: "Armenian Border Trade with Iran Being Set Up"] [Text] Yerevan -- The Armenian Government has authorized the republic's Megrinskiy Rayon to begin border trade with Iran's neighboring province. Meanwhile, even before the official document was signed, Iranian goods had become a permanent feature on the Armenian market. In the very center of Yerevan there is a brisk trade in paraffin stoves, oriental sweetmeats, textiles, and other goods in increased demand.
